  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Static is a 3D-platformer where you control a television-traversing ghost dead set on rescuing their spectral neighbors. Reunite lost spirits and breathe new (after)life into a once-forgotten ghostly neighborhood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937930/extras/bbfa956bdd22d564d4ea12ee0fc18488.poster.avif?t=1734365231\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937930/extras/bbfa956bdd22d564d4ea12ee0fc18488.webm?t=1734365231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937930/extras/bbfa956bdd22d564d4ea12ee0fc18488.mp4?t=1734365231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and explore diverse worlds each with their own distinct themes and challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rescue your ghostly neighbors who have been trapped away inside the worlds behind their television sets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize lightbulbs and other powerups to enhance your spectral abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcome difficult platforming challenges that will test your skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter and face off against a variety of strange, creepy creatures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles and put your ghostly skills to the test</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937930/extras/8aebd77dc73acd3080eb554dfb96a8ee.poster.avif?t=1734365231\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937930/extras/8aebd77dc73acd3080eb554dfb96a8ee.webm?t=1734365231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937930/extras/8aebd77dc73acd3080eb554dfb96a8ee.mp4?t=1734365231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Static is a 3D-platformer where you control a television-traversing ghost dead set on rescuing their spectral neighbors. Reunite lost spirits and breathe new (after)life into a once-forgotten ghostly neighborhood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937930/extras/bbfa956bdd22d564d4ea12ee0fc18488.poster.avif?t=1734365231\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937930/extras/bbfa956bdd22d564d4ea12ee0fc18488.webm?t=1734365231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937930/extras/bbfa956bdd22d564d4ea12ee0fc18488.mp4?t=1734365231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and explore diverse worlds each with their own distinct themes and challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rescue your ghostly neighbors who have been trapped away inside the worlds behind their television sets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize lightbulbs and other powerups to enhance your spectral abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcome difficult platforming challenges that will test your skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter and face off against a variety of strange, creepy creatures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles and put your ghostly skills to the test</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937930/extras/8aebd77dc73acd3080eb554dfb96a8ee.poster.avif?t=1734365231\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https: